text.section:
This section does not apply to:
Any transfer of a used vehicle to any licensed dealer or to any foreign dealer;
Any transfer between:
Spouses;
A parent and child; or
Co-owners of the vehicle to be transferred when a co-owner's name is being removed from the title;
Any transfer of a used vehicle that is not to be both titled and registered in this State;
Any transfer of a used vehicle among any agencies of the State;
Any transfer of a used vehicle as described in § 13-503.2 of this article;
Any transfer of a used vehicle into a written inter vivos trust in which the transferor is the primary beneficiary;
Any transfer of a used island vehicle, as defined in § 13-935 of this article, registered, or to be registered, as a Class K (farm area/island) vehicle; or
Any transfer of an off-highway recreational vehicle.
